d48c			; version 1 - allows for a single stored file to be selected to run at start up (if se storage is enabled) 
d48c			; followed by loading of a list of scripts in eeprom 
d48c			 
d48c			; version 2 - if se storage is enabled then auto load all files which begin with a '*' else use loading 
